        You don't need to instantiate this class since gson automatically instanciate it If you want to use this class you will need to use getModrinthModfromName(String) or getModFromUserId(User)
        Parameters:
        id - The id of your mod
        team - The id of the team that has ownership of this mod
        title - The title or name of the mod
        description - A short description of the mod
        status - The status of the mod - ModStatus
        license - The license of the mod
        client_side - The support range for the client mod - SideStatus
        server_side - The support range for the client mod - SideStatus
        downloads - The total number of downloads the mod has
        categories - A list of the categories that the mod is in
        versions - A list of ids for versions of the mod
        icon_url - The URL of the icon of the mod
        issues_url - An optional link to where to submit bugs or issues with the mod
        source_url - An optional link to the source code for the mod
        wiki_url - An optional link to the mod's wiki page or other relevant information
        discord_url - An optional link to the mod's discord
        donation_url - An optional list of all donation links the mod has
        published - The date that this version was published
        updated - The date at which the mod was updated
